Class BackwardsInterproceduralCFG

  • java.lang.Object
    • soot.jimple.toolkits.ide.icfg.BackwardsInterproceduralCFG
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BiDiInterproceduralCFG<Unit,SootMethod>

    public class BackwardsInterproceduralCFG
extends java.lang.Object
implements BiDiInterproceduralCFG<Unit,SootMethod>
    Same as JimpleBasedInterproceduralCFG but based on inverted unit graphs. This should be used for backward analyses.
